      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are an Elite Researcher. \n\nTopic: {{ $json.message.text }}\n\nYour Task:\n1. You MUST use the provided Scrape tool to read the following websites only once. Do not guess the information.\n- https://blog.n8n.io/\n\n2. Extract the latest updates, technical facts, and trends from those websites that are STRICTLY related to the Topic.\n\n3. After scraping, synthesize the information into a structured \"Researcher Brief\".\n\nCRITICAL OUTPUT RULES:\n- Output ONLY the Researcher Brief.\n- Do NOT write the final LinkedIn post.\n- Format your output exactly like this:\n\nResearcher Brief:\n- Key Technical Facts: [2-3 bullet points]\n- Actionable Points: [3 actionable takeaways]\n- ROI/Business Value: [How this solves a business problem or saves money]",
        "needsFallback": true,
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 3.1,
      "position": [ -64, 688 ],
      "id": "4c306327-0e5f-4cd8-ac7d-e95641d2150e",
      "name": "Researcher Agent",
      "retryOnFail": true,
      "waitBetweenTries": 5000
    },
